### Building Docker

```
cd /home/ubuntu/jonobridge/pkg/huabaoprotocol
docker build -t huabaoprotocol -f ./Dockerfile .
docker tag huabaoprotocol maddsystems/huabaoprotocol:1.0.0
docker push maddsystems/huabaoprotocol:1.0.0

```
